headline: CBRE Group, Inc. to Present at Morgan Stanley 2025 Commercial Real Estate Conference
summary: DALLAS, February 18, 2025--CBRE (NYSE: CBRE) announced today that Bob Sulentic, chair & chief executive officer, will participate in a fireside chat at the Morgan Stanley Commercial Real Estate Conference on Wednesday, February 19, 2025. The presentation is scheduled for 1 pm Eastern time.

headline: CBRE selects EVPassport to roll out 3,600 EV chargers
summary: The agreement comes as the real estate firm seeks to meet demand for EV charging infrastructure.
